            我們將為每位學生提供完整的學習材料，確保學習效果
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          {materialsProvided.map((material, index) => (
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 text-center shadow-lg">
              <div class="text-4xl text-blue-600 mb-4">
                {index === 0 ? "📦" : index === 1 ? "📊" : "📝"}
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">{material}</h3>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Handcraft Products Brochure Button -->
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 rounded-lg p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">手作產品目錄</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">瀏覽完整的手作產品簡介，了解所有STEM手作活動</p>
            <a 
              href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MrvlRJ97L83k4MkKCZ0Z_sjYPCM-lHWW/view?usp=drive_link" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-purple-700 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-0.5"
            >
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
              </svg>
              下載手作活動簡介
